<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="except-conj-prep">except <strong><em>conj &amp; prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'sept/    美 /ɪk'sept/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-apart-from">1.★ <strong>除...外 (apart from)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No pets except fish are permitted in student rooms. 
除了鱼，学生宿舍禁止养其他宠物。</p><footer>2015 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He usually goes to work on his bike except on rainy days. 
除了雨天，他一般都骑自行车上班。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The seaside town is beautiful <strong>except when</strong> it is windy. 
这座海滨小镇很美，除了刮风时。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This suit fi ts me well <strong>except</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) the colour is too bright.
这套衣服我穿着很合身，只不过颜色太艳了。</p></div>

<h3 id="besides-except">辨析 besides, except</h3>
<p>二者都可用作介词；都含有“除…之外”之意。<br />
<strong>besides ** 是“除…之外 (还) 有”的意思。
</strong>except ** 是“除…之外 (不包括在内)”的意思。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All are present except Helen.
除海伦外，大家都到了。(海伦未到)</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="except-for">except for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>除了…外；除去；只是：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His composition is good, except for some spelling mistakes. 
他的这篇作文写得很好，只是有几处拼写错误。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The room is empty except for a bookshelf standing in one corner. 
除了角落里立着一个书架外，房间内空荡荡的。</p><footer>2013 山东</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>exception /ɪk'sepʃn/ n [C] &amp; [U]  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All students <strong>without exception</strong> must take the English examination. 
所有的学生毫无例外，都必须参加英语考试。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't usually lend people money, but in your case I'll <strong>make an exception</strong>.
我一般不借钱给别人，但就你的情况我可以破例。</p></div>

<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Everything was perfect for the picnic except <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the weather.  （2008 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>